identified the species mainly for the black coloured ventral surface of femora that appears in the 
<typeStatus id="827FB2C9FFB8EF7BFC66FD63FBF0FD48" box="[995,1093,726,752]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">holotype</typeStatus>
and in the specimens sampled in 
<collectorName id="F03169BDFFB8EF7BFF36FD4EFE31FCAC" box="[179,388,762,789]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">ParNa Iguaçu. The</collectorName>
individual recorded for 
<collectingCounty id="B41A74E7FFB8EF7BFD15FD4FFC84FCAC" box="[656,817,762,788]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">
Rio 
<collectorName id="F03169BDFFB8EF7BFD3AFD4FFC84FCAC" box="[703,817,762,788]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">de Janeiro</collectorName>
</collectingCounty>
(
<collectionCode id="3BD594AEFFB8EF7BFCBAFD4FFCC0FCAC" box="[831,885,762,788]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">OSF</collectionCode>
) lacks this character, which makes this a doubtful record
</materialsCitation>
.
</paragraph>
